dev/adr/ADR-0.8.16-onnx-embedder-backend.md:5:desc: Adds a cross-vendor ONNX-Runtime BGE-small embedder (OrtBgeEmbedder) as a new impl Embedder in fathomdb-embedder, injected via EmbedderChoice::Caller with zero engine changes. Reaches AMD ROCm / Intel OpenVINO / DirectML that candle cannot. Behind a new onnx-embedder feature; the thin default build and the in-library 1-bit query path are unchanged. Includes the candle<->ONNX equivalence-measurement plan that feeds the 0.8.18 #5 vector-equivalence tolerance.
