dev/adr/ADR-0.6.0-crate-topology.md:31:**B — Four-crate split: `-storage`, `-projection`, `-vector`, `-query`, `-engine` as facade.** Cleanest module boundaries; slowest compile; internal types become public — hard to evolve; multiplies workspace complexity. Layers-on-layers Stop-doing applies.
