dder defaults.\n\nFATHOM to close the loop (SHOT-2 second half): reconcile/confirm Q2/Q4/Q6 -> converged C-1 contract, RATIFIED-pending-HITL. Loop cap = 2 rounds; if not converged, ESCALATE to HITL (do not spiral). Appended locally at the fathomdb-side sub-ledger; NO memex push."}
