   103	
   104	1. **R-FIL-1 / R-FIL-2** — one typed `Filter` contract serving both paths; the
   105	   shipped G10 re-expressed **byte-identically** (RED→GREEN G10 parity; the
   106	   `filter=None → 0.7.2 SQL` pin holds). → D1, D4, D5.
