   114	   `*_unchecked`, parameterized `json_extract` only, server-side path allowlist,
   115	   injection-safety, implicit-AND. → D1, §4 EXCLUDE.
   116	5. **G0 substrate** — `canonical_nodes(kind)` index; active = `superseded_at IS NULL`
   117	   on logical_id-alone (the partition G4 enumerates). → D3.
