   126	## 2. Open questions (the "RED" — each settled below, no bare TBD)
   127	
   128	- **Q1 — Shape of the unified `Filter` type.** Enum? variants? how do G10's four
   129	  fields express, and how does the closed grammar stay closed? *(HITL: Option A.)*
   130	- **Q2 — Field-availability matrix.** For every filterable field, which physical
   131	  store(s) hold it? Is any field resolvable in only ONE store?
